的都是自己人”。第一次交保险的时候简直心头在滴血，就连我这种拖延症晚期患者，在一年半以后也坚决换了某 G 字头知名保险公司。结果回过头来看，价格下降的幅度并没有明显改善，基本是汽车折旧和个人信用记录的正常积累。","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1,"offset":1346},"end":{"line":46,"column":168,"offset":1513}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1,"offset":1346},"end":{"line":46,"column":168,"offset":1513}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"当初把保险办好，所有的手续就都齐了，第二天直接拿着车行给的文件就把牌照办好了。我去看车的时候是开着考驾照租的车去的，买完车我再开回来，他帮我把新车开到我的公寓，然后打电话让嫂子开车接自己回家。这样一想，更为自己之前以小人之心度君子之腹而羞愧。这次朋友买车本来是想推荐给他的，结果前不久看朋友圈才知道他已经换了工作，有点可惜。","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1,"offset":1517},"end":{"line":48,"column":163,"offset":1679}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1,"offset":1517},"end":{"line":48,"column":163,"offset":1679}}},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我想换车——还是算了","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":5,"offset":1687},"end":{"line":50,"column":15,"offset":1697}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1,"offset":1683},"end":{"line":50,"column":15,"offset":1697}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"觉得现在反正住得离学校很近，每天去学校也不需要开车，真正用车的机会也就是每周一次踢球、一次去超市，以及不定期的短途瞎逛。这样的用车场景，小车的油耗优势并不明显，出去玩的时候，有时需要走一些石子路，SUV 的通过性有明显的优势。所以有想要换车的打算。","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1,"offset":1701},"end":{"line":52,"column":125,"offset":1825}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1,"offset":1701},"end":{"line":52,"column":125,"offset":1825}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"但是，上网看了一些车的报价，标价一万五的都是凤毛麟角，两万以上很普遍。这也正常，毕竟绝大多数的 SUV 和 B 级车同平台，本来就比现在的车大一圈，SUV 本身的功能又有溢价。以我现在的存款，肯定是要先卖旧车再买新车，各种标价之外的成本，再想到各种行政手续也要消耗不少的时间和精力，恐怕只能望而却步。","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1,"offset":1829},"end":{"line":54,"column":151,"offset":1979}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1,"offset":1829},"end":{"line":54,"column":151,"offset":1979}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":55,"column":1,"offset":1981}}},"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2018 年初，趁着寒假的功夫考了驾照，趁热打铁买了车，是一辆二手的丰田花冠。","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":2},"end":{"line":2,"column":40,"offset":41}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":2},"end":{"line":2,"column":40,"offset":41}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近有个朋友要买车了，知道我有车，所以来打听一下；碰巧我也临时起意想要换车，之前对买车和养车的花费，虽然一直在记账，但是脑子里是一团糨糊，需要理一理。","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":45},"end":{"line":4,"column":76,"offset":120}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":45},"end":{"line":4,"column":76,"offset":120}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"结果呢，在这篇文章动笔之前，朋友就已经秀出新车的照片了；算完买车的帐之后，我也暂时决定不换车了。所以这篇文章，权当是周更凑数吧。","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":124},"end":{"line":6,"column":65,"offset":188}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":124},"end":{"line":6,"column":65,"offset":188}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"先来算帐"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#先来算帐"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"先来算帐","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":4,"offset":195},"end":{"line":8,"column":8,"offset":199}}}]}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":192},"end":{"line":8,"column":8,"offset":199}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因为隐私的关系，所有价格都是约数，这样可以减小一点点","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":203},"end":{"line":10,"column":27,"offset":229}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2017/12/howto-cover-your-tracks-10.html"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"信息量","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":28,"offset":230},"end":{"line":10,"column":31,"offset":233}}}],"position":{"start":{"li